4. DevOps / Platform Engineering – CloudOps Sentinel
Choice: Multi-Agent
Justification

The first three investigations are completely independent.

They query different systems:

Investigation	Tool
Metrics	Datadog
Deployment Logs	GitHub Actions
DB Performance	AWS RDS

These can execute simultaneously, reducing incident response time.

Afterward:

A Decision Agent aggregates evidence.
If confidence <80%, a Human Approval Gate is triggered.
If approved, a Remediation Agent executes rollback/restart.
Finally, a Communication Agent posts the RCA to Slack.






